(door shuts)

42:33.018 --> 42:34.450
(footsteps crunch)

42:36.721 --> 42:38.454
- Hey.
- Hey.

42:38.456 --> 42:39.923
- Whatcha doin' out here?

42:40.058 --> 42:42.257
- You know,
when you're younger...

42:42.294 --> 42:44.193
<i> - He's been in there</i>
<i> all morning.</i>

42:44.195 --> 42:46.262
<i> It's like he thinks</i>
<i> he's on a date.</i>

42:46.331 --> 42:48.598
I walked in on him doing
this yesterday,

42:48.600 --> 42:51.133
But he said he was just working
through some engine problems.

42:52.604 --> 42:54.870
- Do we know who
he's talking to?

42:54.940 --> 42:57.306
- Yes, he is talking to peggy.

42:59.311 --> 43:00.843
Do you know who peggy is?

43:04.816 --> 43:07.083
- Yeah, um,

43:07.218 --> 43:09.018
Peggy is short for margaret,

43:09.054 --> 43:11.421
And margaret's my mom.

